title: Compulsion
description: Frankie and Graely's story continues in Through Time-Compulsion (early release first week of June)A new threat has entered the mix and once again the Fae find themselves in a position where they have to break their own rule and interfere in the Human Realm. The Dark Princes, Pestale and Hordly find an ally and both Frankie and Graely's love and devotion is challenged.Will hope, love and courage be victorious?Through Time-Compulsion
author: Claudy Conn
